  "description": "Investigate and Fix Missing Hero Background Image on About Page\n\nThe hero section on the About page is displaying empty because the background SVG file (about-hero-bg.svg) is not loading correctly.\n\nRequirements:\n- Verify the file about-hero-bg.svg exists in the expected directory\n- Check that the file path in the About page component is correct (relative vs absolute paths)\n- Ensure the SVG file is properly imported or referenced in the codebase\n- Verify the build process includes SVG files in the output bundle\n- Check browser console for any 404 errors or network failures related to this asset\n- Confirm the CSS/styling correctly applies the background image to the hero section\n- Test the fix across different environments (development, staging, production)\n- Validate the hero section displays the background image correctly after the fix\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- SVG file may have been moved or renamed\n- Build configuration may exclude certain asset types or directories\n- Path resolution may differ between development and production builds\n- Image may be loading but not visible due to CSS issues (z-index, dimensions, positioning)",
